And if you want to add any context, feel free, but the question was any exploration

00:07:38.320 --> 00:07:43.640
of chat GPT to see, uh, to identify any possible or meaningful use.

00:07:44.279 --> 00:07:47.720
It's funny you ask because I think it's a really good question and I think it's

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:50.799
to identify any possible or meaningful use.

00:07:51.399 --> 00:07:52.359
It's funny you ask.

