And just remind people, if you want to use Slido, you can use that link in the

00:08:54.200 --> 00:08:59.479
chat, but somebody had asked earlier, I would love to learn Dara, how you have

00:08:59.479 --> 00:09:04.880
found the transition from computational immunology to finance and operations.

00:09:06.119 --> 00:09:06.719
Yeah.

00:09:06.760 --> 00:09:07.239
Yeah.

00:09:07.280 --> 00:09:11.359
